00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:26.440
Dame Jifu, voici la princesse consort !

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:40.040
Shen Yuanjin,

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.840
Comment oses-tu me frapper ?

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:44.040
